I'm not sure which readme you're referring to, @ndm2 , but maybe I can clarify things with a little bit of code:

```
$config = [
    'host' => ...,
    'port' => ...,
    'database' => ...,
    'username' => ...,
    'password' => ...,
];
$driver = new Cake\Database\Driver\Mysql($config);
$connection = new Cake\Database\Connection([
    'driver' => $driver,
    'log' => false,
]);
$schema = $connection->getSchemaCollection();
$schema->listTables();
```
That's basically the steps we take for establishing and using a DB connection.
